As we’ve seen from the Chinese and Zoroastrian
creation stories, myths often tend to focus

15
00:00:53,310 --> 00:00:58,540
on dualities, or binaries, and one of the
key ones we find is a distinction between

16
00:00:58,540 --> 00:01:00,270
men and women.

17
00:01:00,270 --> 00:01:05,400
And this binary opposition frequently sets
women as subordinate to men, at least on earth.

18
00:01:05,400 --> 00:01:09,210
In the heavens, it’s a little bit more complicated,
as it tends to be.

19
00:01:09,210 --> 00:01:13,219
Let’s start with a story that is probably
well known to many of our viewers: the creation

20
00:01:13,219 --> 00:01:15,619
