53
00:03:05,640 --> 00:03:09,909
Whether this describes a family structure
that already existed or was written in order

54
00:03:09,909 --> 00:03:14,670
to encourage such a family structure, we can’t
say for certain, but it’s likely that this

55
00:03:14,670 --> 00:03:16,790
was an after-the-fact description.

56
00:03:16,790 --> 00:03:20,680
Providing a rationalization for what people
encounter in their daily lives is an important

57
00:03:20,680 --> 00:03:21,680
